    <p><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/eleventy-plugin-hubspot">This plugin</a> adds shortcodes to your Eleventy project to easily embed <a href="https://www.hubspot.com/">HubSpot</a> forms and meetings calendars.</p>

    <h2>Installation</h2>
    <p>Install the plugin from npm:</p>
    <pre><code>npm install eleventy-plugin-hubspot --save-dev</code></pre>

    <h2>Configuration</h2>
    <p>Add it to your <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/docs/config/">Eleventy Config</a> file:</p>
    <h3>ESM (Eleventy 3.x+)</h3>
    <pre><code>import eleventyPluginHubspot from 'eleventy-plugin-hubspot';

export default function (eleventyConfig) {
    eleventyConfig.addPlugin(eleventyPluginHubspot, {
        portalId: 1234567
    });
}</code></pre>
    <h3>CommonJS (Eleventy 2.x)</h3>
    <pre><code>const eleventyPluginHubspot = require('eleventy-plugin-hubspot');

module.exports = function (eleventyConfig) {
    eleventyConfig.addPlugin(eleventyPluginHubspot, {
        portalId: 1234567
    });
};</code></pre>

    <h2>Options</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><code>portalId</code> - <strong>(required)</strong> Your HubSpot portal ID</li>
        <li><code>loadingMode</code> - Loading strategy: <code>default</code>, <code>eager</code>, <code>interact</code>, or <code>lazy</code><br/><small>Default: <code>default</code></small></li>
        <li><code>loadingSpinner</code> - Custom spinner HTML or <code>false</code> to disable<br/><small>Default: built-in SVG spinner</small></li>
        <li><code>scriptAttributes</code> - Object of custom attributes for the HubSpot script tag (e.g., OneTrust bypass)<br/><small>Default: <code>{}</code></small></li>
        <li><code>locale</code> - Form language locale<br/><small>Default: <code>undefined</code></small></li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Loading Modes</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><code>default</code> - Form loads immediately with the page</li>
        <li><code>eager</code> - Form loads on <code>DOMContentLoaded</code></li>
        <li><code>interact</code> - Form loads on first user interaction (best for performance)</li>
        <li><code>lazy</code> - Form loads when scrolled into viewport</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Usage</h2>
    <h3>HubSpot Forms</h3>
    <pre><code>{% raw %}{% hubspotForm "your-form-id" %}

{# With options #}
{% hubspotForm "your-form-id", { locale: "es" } %}{% endraw %}</code></pre>

    <h3>HubSpot Meetings</h3>
    <pre><code>{% raw %}{% hubspotMeetings "https://meetings.hubspot.com/your-meeting-link" %}{% endraw %}</code></pre>

    <h2>Demo</h2>
